The expression formula_242 is called the &quot;covariant derivative of formula_243 with respect to formula_244&quot;.

=== Levi-Civita connection ===
Two Riemannian manifolds with different connections have different geometry. Thankfully, there is a natural connection associated to a Riemannian manifold called the Levi-Civita connection.

A connection formula_245 is said to &quot;preserve the metric&quot; if
: formula_246
A connection formula_245 is &quot;torsion-free&quot; if
